1. Dobrodošlicu želim svim gostima našeg hotela. (I welcome all guests of our hotel.)

2. Svoju dobrodošlicu želim iskazati novim kolegama u firmi. (I want to express my welcome to the new colleagues in the company.)

3. Naš gradonačelnik izrazio je dobrodošlicu svim učesnicima konferencije. (Our mayor welcomed all participants of the conference.)

4. Uz dobrodošlicu su nam ponuđeni kolači i piće. (We were offered cakes and drinks as a welcome.)

5. Nismo dobili dobrodošlicu od komšija kada smo se uselili u novu kuću. (We didn't receive a welcome from our neighbors when we moved into our new house.)

6. Gosti su nam priređeni veliku dobrodošlicu uz tradicionalnu muziku i ples. (The guests were given a warm welcome with traditional music and dance.)

7. Poslovni partneri su izrazili dobrodošlicu našoj delegaciji na aerodromu. (Business partners welcomed our delegation at the airport.)

8. Ova turistička agencija pruža dobrodošlicu svojim klijentima u mnogim zemljama sveta. (This travel agency provides a welcome to its clients in many countries around the world.)

9. Bez dobrodošlice i ljubaznosti, usluga ne može biti potpuna. (Without a welcome and kindness, the service cannot be complete.)

10. Dobrodošlicu su nam poželjeli i predstavnici lokalne zajednice. (We were also welcomed by representatives of the local community.)